<cb:div>
<pb n="0041a" xml:id="I01.0015.0041a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="I" n="0041a00" type="honorific"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><cb:docNumber>No. 15</cb:docNumber>
<lb ed="I" n="0041a00" type="honorific"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><title>張安世造像記</title></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb ed="I" n="0041a01" type="honorific"/><p xml:id="pI01p0041a0101">神龕　　　　　　乙未八月己亥
<lb ed="I" n="0041a02" type="honorific"/>　癸巳為皇帝陛下。七世父母。<note n="0041001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30421"/>＝所【史】</note><app n="0041001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">所</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30421"/></rdg></app>生父母。一切眾
<lb ed="I" n="0041a03" type="honorific"/>　生告<note n="0041002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30422"/>＝訖【史】</note><app n="0041002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">訖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30422"/></rdg></app>。夫大<note n="0041003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30433"/>＝聖【史】</note><app n="0041003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30433"/></rdg></app>幽<note n="0041004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30424"/>＝微【史】</note><app n="0041004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30424"/></rdg></app>。以<note n="0041005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30308"/>＝虛【史】</note><app n="0041005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>寂為旨。生<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">成</unclear>
<lb ed="I" n="0041a04" type="honorific"/>　萬物。功不在己。纖萇通<app type="star" corresp="#0041004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">微</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30424"/></rdg></app>。咸無不周。大<app type="star" corresp="#0041003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">聖</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30433"/></rdg></app>
<lb ed="I" n="0041a05" type="honorific"/>　如味。而研之者明。至言若訥。<note n="0041006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">寻＝尋【史】</note><app n="0041006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">尋</lem><rdg wit="【原】">寻</rdg></app>之者辨。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a06" type="honorific"/>　當今皇帝御世。万<note n="0041007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">𨛁＝邦【史】</note><app n="0041007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">邦</lem><rdg wit="【原】">𨛁</rdg></app>斯順。善化垂範。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a07" type="honorific"/>　群迷心返。伏聞一念之善。獲無盡
<lb ed="I" n="0041a08" type="honorific"/>　之功。一米投<note n="0041008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30427"/>＝廚【史】</note><app n="0041008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">廚</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30427"/></rdg></app>。致恒沙之果。是以張安
<lb ed="I" n="0041a09" type="honorific"/>　　世。體識<app type="star" corresp="#0041005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">虛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30308"/></rdg></app>空。識真正法。減<note n="0041009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30428"/>＝割【史】</note><app n="0041009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">割</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30428"/></rdg></app>家珍。張
<lb ed="I" n="0041a10" type="honorific"/>　安世人身造石像一區。上願帝主康寧。祚延
<lb ed="I" n="0041a11" type="honorific"/>　無窮。若洛三徒。不逕八難。下願張安世人身家
<lb ed="I" n="0041a12" type="honorific"/>　眷。合無大小。無病少<note n="0041010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30430"/>＝痛【史】</note><app n="0041010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">痛</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30430"/></rdg></app>。延年益<note n="0041011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30923"/>＝壽【史】</note><app n="0041011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">壽</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30923"/></rdg></app>。宅舍全
<lb ed="I" n="0041a13" type="honorific"/>　<note n="0041012" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig"><g ref="#CB30432"/>＝鋼【史】</note><app n="0041012"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鋼</lem><rdg wit="【原】"><g ref="#CB30432"/></rdg></app>。來財宜寶。用之無盡。所願從心。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a14" type="honorific"/>　祖張豐洛。父周慶。叔父雙慶。兄文虯。兄文清。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a15" type="honorific"/>　　　　　　　　　　　　兄賢黃。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a16" type="honorific"/>　名安世。息還洛。息阿僧。息僧歡。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a17" type="honorific"/>　妻李男異。妾王阿引。息富洛。息雙富。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a18" type="honorific"/>　姪阿洛。姪阿歡。姪阿奴。姪天還。姪似仁。
<lb ed="I" n="0041a19" type="honorific"/>　姪德仁。姪□歡。</p>
